AutoEmbed - Audio/Video embed snippet generator
-----------------------------------------------

AutoEmbed is a PHP class that parses media information from a given URL.

Project page: http://code.google.com/p/autoembed/

Synopsis:
---------

$ae = new AutoEmbed();

// Parse a new URL
if (!$ae->parseURL('http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z3U0udLH974')) {
	// No video found or site is not supported
}

// Extract the media's object params
$object_params = $ae->getObjectParams();

// Extract the media's flash params
$flash_params = $ae->getFlashParams();

// Construct HTML tag for embedding the video
$embed_tag = $ae->getEmbedCode();

Supported Video Sites
---------------------

List of supported video sites coming soon.
